FIFA World Cup Match Insights
Comprehensive Analysis of FIFA World Cup Matches (1930–2022)

This repository contains an end‑to‑end analysis of the FIFA World Cup Match Insights dataset sourced from Kaggle. It includes data exploration, performance metrics, match statistics, and visual dashboards summarizing 90+ years of World Cup history.

Dataset Source:
https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/saadaliyaseen/fifa-world-cup-match-insights
Project Overview
This project analyzes historical FIFA World Cup match data to uncover trends in:

Total goals scored

Match outcomes (home wins, away wins, draws)

Goal differences

Win percentages

Team‑wise performance

Stage‑wise match statistics

The analysis is supported by visual dashboards similar to the ones shown in the included PDF (Power BI report).
